        "message": "Add Korean documentation (README.ko.md) (#18)\n\n* docs(ko): README 목차·0x00 42 소개 번역 및 앵커\n\n* docs(ko): README 0x01~0x06 및 흔한 실수 0x00 서두\n\n* docs(ko): README 흔한 실수 1장 대부분 번역\n\n* docs(ko): 클린 코드·에필로그 일부 및 remote_challenges README 번역\n\n* docs(ko): README 장 제목·앵커(도구·자료·튜토리얼) 및 미번역 안내\n\n* docs: add English README (README.en.md) and language switchers\n\nMade-with: Cursor\n\n* docs: split README into Korean (README.md) and English (README.en.md) with language switcher\n\n- Export original English README from pre-translation snapshot (beb30aa~1)\n- Add language switcher banner at the top of both README.md and README.en.md\n- README.md: Korean version (existing translated content)\n- README.en.md: English version (original content preserved)\n\nCo-authored-by: LEEHYUNBIN <Leehyunbin0131@users.noreply.github.com>\n\n* docs: default README in English; Korean in README.ko.md\n\nMade-with: Cursor\n\n* Fix README language headers and Korean/English cross-links\n\nREADME.md had contradictory language banners and a Korean subtitle above\nEnglish body text. README.en.md linked Korean to README.md instead of\nREADME.ko.md. Align headers with content and correct navigation.\n\nMade-with: Cursor\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>\nCo-authored-by: LEEHYUNBIN <Leehyunbin0131@users.noreply.github.com>",
